node.title: Man dies in hospital after boat flipped in Pauanui
node.description: Two children remain in Starship Hospital in a critical but stable condition.
node.content: ["A man who was onboard the boat that overturned at Pauanui yesterday has died, police have confirmed.", "Two children remain in Starship Hospital in a critical but stable condition.", "Police and Maritime NZ are continuing to investigate the circumstances that led to the incident.", "This includes making enquiries in relation to the death on behalf of the Coroner."]
